Package com.telenav.kivakit.service.registry.protocol.discover

Class DiscoverServicesRequest

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.service.registry.protocol.BaseRequest
com.telenav.kivakit.service.registry.protocol.discover.DiscoverServicesRequest
public class DiscoverServicesRequest extends BaseRequest
Requests information about registered services within a given scope. If the request type is DiscoverServicesRequest.SearchType.ALL_SERVICES, the all services within the scope are returned. For DiscoverServicesRequest.SearchType.APPLICATION_SERVICES, the services of a particular application are returned. And if the request type is DiscoverServicesRequest.SearchType.SERVICES_OF_TYPE, then all the services of a given type are returned. The individual values that must be provided as properties depend on the request type.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
